Installation:
    git clone git://github.com/iknite/vimconfig.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:
	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:
    cd ~/.vim
	git submodule init
	git submodule update

Create the proper mac terminal installation:
	brew install macvim
	brew linkapps
	mvim -v
	alias vim="mvim -v"

ACTUAL SUBMODULES:
	snipmate
	surround
	fugutive
	php-vim
	
